{"problem_id": "prime__prime_decomp_correct", "source": "mathcomp_project", "difficulty": "long", "theorem_name": "prime_decomp_correct", "path": "/Users/gbaudart/Project/llm4rocq/math-comp/boot/prime.v", "prefix_chars": 8679, "prefix_lines": 187, "statement": "Lemma prime_decomp_correct :\n  let pd_val pd := \\prod_(f <- pd) pfactor f.1 f.2 in\n  let lb_dvd q m := ~~ has [pred d | d %| m] (index_iota 2 q) in\n  let pf_ok f := lb_dvd f.1 f.1 && (0 < f.2) in\n  let pd_ord q pd := path ltn q (unzip1 pd) in\n  let pd_ok q n pd := [/\\ n = pd_val pd, all pf_ok pd & pd_ord q pd] in\n  forall n, n > 0 -> pd_ok 1 n (prime_decomp n).", "gt_proof_sentences": 121}
